#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:163
msgid "Behold the encampment to the north! Orcs gather there. No doubt they mean to seize Erzen for themselves."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:175
msgid "<i>Brother, are the preparations complete?</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:179
msgid "<i>You need not remind me. Everything proceeds according to our design.</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:183
msgid "The fate of this fortress lies in our hands. To arms!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:196
msgid "At last, the ritual is complete. Now we may transcend the boundaries of life and death... all shall bend to our will."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:251
msgid "These... these are the undead? You have violated the most sacred of taboos. This evil surpasses even that of the orcs."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:256
msgid "I shall return with reinforcements. We will purge not only the orcs, but your foul presence as well."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:298
msgid "Prepare to meet your doom, necromancers!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:316
msgid "Look how these humans turn upon themselves. Now is our moment to strike!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:324
msgid "Brother, what course shall we take?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:328
msgid "This land has grown too small for my ambitions. Too many vermin stand in my path. I shall depart... but your journey ends here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:352
msgid "Foolish brother! Know that you are not the only one destined to endure!"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:367
msgid "Move Gwiti to the escape route"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:393
msgid "I cannot fall here! Soon I shall return with an army at my back, and you shall all be destroyed!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:408
msgid "Argh! Our lord shall have vengeance upon you all!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:421
msgid "Rise from the depths of death!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:446
msgid "I... shall obey... master..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:451
msgid "Scout the enemy positions and create diversions. Now go!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Blucyn
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:484
msgid "Rally the reinforcements! We must not let them escape!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/01_Double_Betrayal.cfg:510
msgid "You should never have let me fall. Without me, you are nothing."
msgstr ""

