#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:148
msgid "A sudden tempest seized the vessel bearing Gwiti and Nati."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:153
msgid "The ship splintered apart."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:161
msgid "Yet the brothers’ tale was not to end there."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:200
msgid "Do I... still draw breath?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:215
msgid "I have washed ashore, it seems... but Nati is nowhere to be found."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:247
msgid "My shackles lie broken. Perhaps the dark gods have not wholly forsaken me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [unit]: id=Arkal-Thil, type=Dark Adept
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:252
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:271
msgid "Arkal-Thil"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:253
msgid "I sense the shadow of darkness within you..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:266
msgid "Who addresses me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:290
msgid "I am a sorcerer, Arkal-Thil by name."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:294
msgid "You are a necromancer, like myself... are you not?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:298
msgid "Indeed. Will you be our salvation? These grounds once served as sanctuary for our cult. But savage beasts descended upon us, devouring most of our number. We lacked the strength to repel them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:302
msgid "They await only destruction at my hands. Soon they shall serve me eternally as undying warriors."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:307
msgid "We are grateful, new master. We pledge ourselves to you. Now is the hour of vengeance and bloodshed!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Xabrak
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:335
msgid "Look there! The necromancer assails us with his skeletal legion! But strange... we thought we had destroyed them all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Grakarat
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:339
msgid "How I relish crushing their bones! Let battle be joined!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:373
msgid "Who languishes in this cage?"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: id=Gabtur, type=Death Squire
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:380
msgid "Gabtur"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:396
msgid "One of our brothers! They slew him once already!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gabtur
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:401
msgid "Danger lurks here... This is the den of the savages who slew me and imprisoned my spirit."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:406
msgid "Gabtur, it is I! We have found a new master. Already most of the beasts lie dead at our feet!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:411
msgid "Join my uprising. I shall grant you power beyond measure."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:428
msgid "Gwiti — you must not tarry. Your destiny beckons."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:432
msgid "What? Who dares speak to my very thoughts? Reveal yourself!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:436
msgid "Your brother Nati also treads this land. You must confront him, for only one Ha’atel shall survive this crucible."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:440
msgid "Impossible! I shall not be the one to fall!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:457
msgid "Death comes for all naga who dare stand in my path!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:467
msgid "I am... vanquished..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:483
msgid "Who lurks in the shadows?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:497
msgid "Master... I return to you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:502
msgid "How came you to this place?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:507
msgid "I followed your final command faithfully."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:512
msgid "You were scouting far from the battlefield when disaster struck. Is that what you mean to tell me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gadash
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:517
msgid "I sensed your dark power upon this shore. The journey to return to your side was long, but now I stand ready to serve once more."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/02_A_New_Chance.cfg:526
msgid "The Wesnothians have discovered my escape! All is lost..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=03_Brother_Against_Brother
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:5
msgid "Brother Against Brother"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:32
msgid "Defeat your brother Nati Ha’atel"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:106
msgid "As the crimson light of dusk painted the horizon, Gwiti discovered his arch-rival and brother, Nati, had already taken position nearby — their long-standing animosity about to reach its inevitable conclusion."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:112
msgid "Ah, loathed brother mine. Gaze well upon this setting sun, for it shall be the last you shall witness in these lands."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:116
msgid "These lands? Your ignorance betrays you more thoroughly than your words ever could."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:120
msgid "You, who fled like a coward at Erzen, dare speak of ignorance?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:124
msgid "Cease your hollow boasting. You are but a shadow of what I once deemed a worthy opponent."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:128
msgid "But the darkness shall prove my strength... You must fall."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:132
msgid "I will crush you with all the might that has always set me apart. Flee now, or be annihilated."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:157
msgid "Your scalp shall make a fitting trophy."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:161
msgid "Master, will you truly destroy your own brother?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:166
msgid "Blood ties mean nothing when destiny calls. Would you hesitate in my place?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:170
msgid "... I suppose not, master."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:178
msgid "Your doom draws near!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:189
msgid "His forces are but a disorganized rabble, barely worth our concern. Our victory is inevitable."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:193
msgid "As you command, let us see it through."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:198
msgid "Face your brother, necromancer. Your true power lies not in blood, but in the darkness you command."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:201
msgid "You again... Who are you, that speaks from the shadows?"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:203
msgid "One who knows the path of true power. Prove yourself worthy."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:210
msgid "Witness your final moments, you miserable wretch. Know that it is only by my mercy you still bask in the light of the sun. Before it sets, you shall meet your end."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:214
msgid "Let me remind you that even now, my undead legions march forth, eager to embrace you in death. Your fate is sealed."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:225
msgid "My foolish brother... Our destiny was written the moment we drew breath. You merely prolong the inevitable."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:229
msgid "Is that your final testament? I shall continue my vengeance against Wesnoth. Prepare yourself for what comes after."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:233
msgid "It is over... I am doomed... I am undone."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:249
msgid "Burn to ash, all who stand in my path!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/03_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:262
msgid "Die, and be forgotten!"
msgstr ""

