#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:192
msgid "And so, Gwiti set his sights upon the Tower of Kaleon, where the greatest magi of the age had once studied and guarded their arcane secrets."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:197
msgid "If my memory serves, that structure in the distance must indeed be the Tower of Kaleon. The ancient spells and knowledge stored within will soon be mine — and with them, my power shall grow vast enough to crush Wesnoth."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quirind
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:204
msgid "A dark sorcerer draws near! Could it truly be the same one we cast out long ago?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quirind
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:208
msgid "Accursed practitioner of death, know that we, the magi of Kaleon, guardians of this tower, shall defend it to our final breath! Turn back now, or face ruin."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lessalin
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:213
msgid "Fear not, Quirind. By ancient accord, the elves shall stand with you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urind
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:217
msgid "Vile conjurer, this ground is no place for your kind. Leave, or we shall banish you to the abyss!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:221
msgid "Ignorant fools... you are blind to your own doom. All who stand before me shall fall."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:225
msgid "Master, the snow grows heavy. If we delay, we risk being buried alive!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:469
msgid "Curse it all! I am undone, and the tower stands unguarded!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:491
msgid "Quirind, we have failed... you must keep the tower safe!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:508
msgid "Ha! The tower’s secrets are within my grasp at last!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lessalin
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:512
msgid "A pox upon that wretched sorcerer!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:525
msgid "The path is clear! Press onward!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quirind
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/05_Mages_and_Elves.cfg:546
msgid "Ha! The tower’s wards have awakened — you cannot pass without knowledge to rival ours!"
