#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Shadow_Returns/episode1/scenarios/06_Inside_the_Tower.cfg:167
msgid "Does it unnerve you, Arkal-Thil? Let it feed your dread... soon, that power shall belong to us."
