msgid "Though gifted in the ancient arts, Elynia’s mastery remains unfinished — a journey cut tragically short when darkness claimed her mentor’s life. The sacred magic flows strong within her, yet each spell carries the bitter weight of that loss. Her ethereal beauty masks a heart tempered by battle and grief, her eyes reflecting not merely power, but an unwavering resolve born from witnessing the price of failure. Now she stands as guardian of these lands, though she knows not the true scope of the realm she must protect."
