#. [unit_type]: id=Deathmaster, race=human
#: The_Shadow_Returns/units/undead/Deathmaster.cfg:18
msgid "Through his descent into darkness, Ha’atel has attained powers forbidden to mortal kind, yet at a terrible cost: the undead to whom he pledged his soul now steadily claim his mortal form. As time’s dark tide flows ever onward, he inches closer to becoming that which he commands — a true being of undeath, an abomination to all that draw breath."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=Demilich, race=undead
#: The_Shadow_Returns/units/undead/Demilich.cfg:4
