msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=Demilich, race=undead
#: The_Shadow_Returns/units/undead/Demilich.cfg:24
msgid "The transformation has taken its toll, as Ha’atel’s form now exists between life and death. His flesh grows ever colder while his powers reach horrifying new heights. With each ritual performed, the boundary between master and servant blurs further, as the whispers of the dead guide his hand. Those who witness his passing speak only of shadows that writhe with unnatural life, and of darkness that pulses with its own heartbeat."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=Dread Lich, race=undead
#: The_Shadow_Returns/units/undead/Dread_Lich.cfg:4
msgid "Dread Lich"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=Dread Lich, race=undead
#: The_Shadow_Returns/units/undead/Dread_Lich.cfg:25
msgid "At the culmination of his shadowed pilgrimage, Ha’atel made the ultimate sacrifice to the darkness that had long embraced him, crossing the threshold into immortality itself. At the zenith of his power, he transcended his mortal coil to become a lich — the very embodiment of mortal terror awakened. In this transformation, he crossed a boundary from which there could be no return. Perhaps the cold comfort of immortality and boundless power serves as solace for all he has surrendered in its pursuit."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=Initiate, race=human
#: The_Shadow_Returns/units/undead/Initiate.cfg:4
